                    <p><span style="font-weight: bold;">&lt;nomeGruppo&gt;</span>, <span style="font-weight: bold;"><a href="Monitoraggio__grafico_HACCP_e_storico.htm">Grafico storico</a></span></p>
                </td>
                <td colspan="1" rowspan="1" style="width: 294px;padding-right: 10px;padding-left: 10px;background-color: #eaeaea;border-right-width: 3px;border-right-style: Solid;border-right-color: #ffffff;border-bottom-width: 3px;border-bottom-color: #ffffff;border-bottom-style: Solid;" bgcolor="#EAEAEA" width="294px">
